# Ignore common IDE and system files
.idea/
.vscode/
*.suo
*.ntvsca
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Environment and config sensitive files
# config.php contains database credentials. In a real-world scenario, we would ignore it and use config.example.php or .env
# However, for this project submission, keeping config.php committed is usually expected so it runs out-of-the-box.
# We will not ignore config.php here to facilitate evaluation, but we will ignore any temp/cache files.

# Logs and databases
*.log
sqlite.db
